description:
This is a 18 minute workout called '15 MIN FULL BODY STRETCH & COOL DOWN ROUTINE' from the channel MadFit.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Stretching and Cardio/Mat.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Reboot Workout and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: A quick and simple beginner flexibility routine that can be done in 15 minutes! Use this as a daily total body stretch, or as a cool down after workouts!
